# House Rent Prediction

## Overview

This project predicts house rental prices using Machine Learning techniques. The model is trained on housing data and estimates rent based on various property features.

## Features

* Data preprocessing and cleaning
* Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
* Feature selection
* Machine Learning model training
* Rent price prediction
* Performance evaluation

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Pandas
* NumPy
* Matplotlib
* Scikit-learn

## Input Features

* Location
* Area (Square Feet)
* Number of Bedrooms
* Number of Bathrooms
* Property Type
* Other relevant housing features

## Outcome

The model predicts the expected rental price of a property based on the provided inputs.

## Learning Outcomes

* Data preprocessing
* Machine Learning workflows
* Predictive analytics
* Model evaluation and optimization
